                <p> The applicant clicks on either contact an agent or Hire Agent button. </p>
            </h6>
            <h6><b>STEP 2</b></h6>
            <h6>
                <p>It takes him to a page to input his email and password and they click on the pay button.</p>
            </h6>
            <h6><b>STEP 3</b></h6>
            <h6>
                <p>It redirects the applicant to paystack payment gateway to pay the stipulated amount.</p>
